==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Remurmur
<hw>Re*mur"mur</hw> <pr>(r?-m?r"m?r)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos>
<ety>[Pref. <ets>re-</ets> + <ets>murmur</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>remurmurare</ets>.]</ety> <def>To murmur again; to utter back, or
reply, in murmurs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The trembling trees, in every plain and wood,⟦br⟧
Her fate <qex>remurmur</qex> to the silver flood.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ren</ent>⟦br⟧
